---
layout: base.njk
title: Транспорт
description: Хладилен автопарк за контролирани доставки
permalink: /transport/
pagination:
    data: products
    size: 1000
    alias: fleet
---

<section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col gap-8">
        <div class="w-full text-left">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[#25425E]">Нашият хладилен автопарк</h1>
            <p class="mt-3 text-primary-deepsea max-w-3xl">Изберете подходящото превозно средство според товара, температурния диапазон и дестинацията. Всички камиони и бусове са оборудвани със системи за мониторинг и документиране на студената верига.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-8 pt-8">
            {% for vehicle in fleet %}
            <div class="group relative">
                <div class="home-product-card h-full p-2 bg-white rounded-3xl relative flex flex-col w-full transition-all duration-300 shadow-md">
                    <div class="home-product-image flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="{{ vehicle.images[0] | url }}" alt="{{ vehicle.title }}" class=""/>
                    </div>

                    <div class="py-3 flex flex-col gap-4 flex-grow">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 justify-between">
                            <h3 class="text-md font-bold text-[#25425E]">{{ vehicle.title }}</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-primary-deepsea leading-relaxed">{{ vehicle.short_description }}</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-primary-volcanic/80">
                            {% if vehicle.temperature_range %}
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2 bg-[#25425E]/5 rounded-2xl px-3 py-2">
                                    <span class="font-semibold text-[#25425E]">Температура</span>
                                    <span>{{ vehicle.temperature_range }}</span>
                                </div>
                            {% endif %}
                            {% if vehicle.capacity %}
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2 bg-[#25425E]/5 rounded-2xl px-3 py-2">
                                    <span class="font-semibold text-[#25425E]">Капацитет</span>
                                    <span>{{ vehicle.capacity }}</span>
                                </div>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>

                        <div class="mt-2 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                            <a href="{{ ('/transport/' ~ vehicle.meta_title ~ '/') | url }}" class="block text-center rounded-full border border-[#25425E] text-[#25425E] font-semibold py-2 mt-auto transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-[#25425E] hover:text-white">Виж детайли</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


